{"title":"朋友是老夏的——×机关见闻","authors":["亚群"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":4,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友是老夏的——×机关见闻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚群  诗  江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友是老夏的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热情是大家的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话题是随手拣的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随手拣来又随手扔掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不觉得可惜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光是宇宙的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗子是大楼的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光从窗子进来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再从窗子出去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也没在意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"局长是上边的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导是大家的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"局长很欢喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"局长欢喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家自然也不生气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友是老夏的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老夏是同事的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有“智者”曰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间是公家的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公家的时间长在大家脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“智者”又曰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老化”是自己的"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}